{"tid":1515993,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[學術討論] 心理戰-十點鳩嗌加強版","createTime":"2019-08-29T11:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T14:47:03.000Z","uid":50598,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d42a379c593160ae7f1ca8631b14ffc289fcbe98","tid":1515993,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:37:28.000Z","msg":"小弟最近發左個夢<br />\n夢到有人每晚十點鳩嗌行動 除左嗌光復香港 時代革命<br />\n有多五分鐘 只嗌侮辱 挑釁黑警既字句 eg. 警察死全家、黑警還眼<br />\n唔係隻隻黑社會都有警察宿舍住 梗有個住你左近<br />\n此舉可以<br />\n1. 俾到心理壓力休班警 做到十面埋伏既壓迫感<br />\n2. 做到社區杯葛 令佢家人覺得羞恥, 試想像下 佢小朋友問：爸爸 爸爸 點解警察要死全家既 <br />\n係幾大既心理陰影面積<br />\n如配合老豆搵仔 嗌出個人資料更加不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無心理學既巴絲討論下人面對咁既情況會點？ <br />\n<br />\n利伸：此帖全為學術討論 絕不鼓吹任何犯法、侮辱警員既行為<br />\n好驚暴徒會拎左黎用 求大家唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9709a8099bf04477885a591ae744998bd0d7262b","tid":1515993,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"開錯台添 應該學術台先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e6c229c599b2c323b19797bbe5eecaa127bb91","tid":1515993,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:40:28.000Z","msg":"9月1"},{"pid":"47b27cbb6fd2e7ec84544d0d48f904c6323545c7","tid":1515993,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"連登無人學術討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59a2a22e8a745db1598fcd4ef95362cda6967c3","tid":1515993,"uid":87068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"請戴頭盔<br />\n加返&ldquo;我好驚&rdquo;三隻字喺句子前"},{"pid":"bfc64175d0964bca874bf0cad3487757d37cc8ff","tid":1515993,"uid":119271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab0d1131dcef685daba449ee5829323752d73bf","tid":1515993,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"屋企附近有狗舍更加要嗌「黑警OT 老婆3P」<br />\n但又會有啲語言潔癖撚話會教壞細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df427a06f218ef7ff11d9fae43e7c567a38d2366","tid":1515993,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cce11cae5b4c6563aab80e57d5f204c10c410f9","tid":1515993,"uid":92038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:11:20.000Z","msg":"首先你要確保隔離鄰舍啲狗唔知啲聲來自邊d單位<br />\n確保安全<br />\n<br />\n所以越多人嗌越好<br />\n<br />\n其次係辱罵黑警此舉其實對警察造成嘅傷害都係精神折磨 同激化佢家庭內嘅糾紛<br />\n<br />\n反而要留意會唔會刺激到激進藍絲 <br />\n你知啦依家撐政府=攞正牌殺人<br />\n<br />\n建議大家除左鬧黑警 可以嘅話開埋大廈單位 令佢地不安 用恐懼籠罩佢地<br />\n<br />\n玩埋電視劇入邊嗰啲變聲器就更好 用啲佢地熟悉但不常見嘅聲音加劇佢地嘅不安 要令到佢地腦內不自覺地loop 摧毀佢地嘅精神<br />\n<br />\n至於聲調 聲量 頻率就更進階 想知再講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上純屬鳩噏 提下意見去探討精神世界 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乖嘅朋友千其唔好試</span></strong>"},{"pid":"607cf34bd488c72a4dd62ca63402a84dfe6b01f4","tid":1515993,"uid":83785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d49735c245eda708ab7b534ec1b8887dd5aaab77","tid":1515993,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGbnrz0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGbnrz0.gif&h=dd99b35f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Cu4EU1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Cu4EU1.gif&h=5bf81da8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"940e1facd705a4342d49254278b41842ee0b1854","tid":1515993,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"如果係咁 唔好叫黑警死全家 佢地對黑警呢個term冇咩認同<br />\n要講就講警察死_ _ 警察 _ _ _<br />\n咁佢地先